    "headline": "Snowflake Summit 26 Puts Governed Enterprise AI At Center Stage",
    "summary": "Snowflake (NYSE:SNOW) used its Snowflake Summit 26 event to roll out a broad set of AI focused product launches and ecosystem integrations. The company highlighted new AI capabilities such as Horizon Context, CoWork enhancements, and Datastream aimed at production grade enterprise AI. Snowflake also announced deeper partnerships with firms including Anthropic, Cognizant, Collibra, Ataccama, RelationalAI, and ThoughtSpot. Customer case studies from companies such as Sanofi and Thomson Reuters...",
